name: Letoya Jessie
description: I am extremely independent and spontaneous. I would have to describe myself as complex but not complicated. I’ve been told, I am sexy and smart but who hasn’t been told that, whether it is true or not?.(I can be romantic and affectionate with the right person. I am also very athletic and I have a goofy sense of humor. I consider myself easy going, energetic and thoughtful. I love to do outdoor adventurous activity, but also enjoy being a "homebody". I’m well-rounded, I enjoy the theater, comedy shows, live music, concerts, museums, movies and book stores. I love sports(watching or playing) I am always open to trying new things.
